You have credentialed access to the Jira Data Center REST API as the user who triggered this conversation:

  - Base URL: $JIRA_DC_BASE_URL
  - Auth:     Authorization: Bearer $JIRA_DC_TOKEN

The token value is supplied only as a sandbox secret/environment variable. These instructions intentionally refer to the variable name, not the secret value.

