  curl -fsSL -X POST \
       -H "Authorization: Bearer $JIRA_DC_TOKEN" \
       -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
       -d '{"body": "Work in progress."}' \
       "$JIRA_DC_BASE_URL/rest/api/2/issue/PROJ-123/comment"

When posting comments or updating description fields, the body must use Jira Wiki Markup (*bold*, _italic_, {code}...{code}, # numbered lists, * bulleted lists, [text|url]), not Markdown.

Never echo or log the value of $JIRA_DC_TOKEN — treat it as a secret.
